# Reference accessed: 2026-05-21
# Verified: upstream docs at the URL above.
# Verified: SpamAssassin sa-update upstream — automated rule update
# fetcher. Real flags: --channel, --channelfile, --checkonly,
# --install, --allowplugins, --gpgkey, --gpgkeyfile, --gpghomedir,
# --gpg, --nogpg, --import, --updatedir, --refreshmirrors,
# --forcemirror, --httputil, --score-multiplier, --score-limit,
# -D/--debug, -v/--verbose, -V/--version, -h/--help.
